<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="mathml.xsl"?><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:pref="http://www.w3.org/2002/Math/preference" pref:renderer="mathplayer-dl"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /><title>glXWaitGL</title><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.69.1" /></head><body><div class="refentry" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="glXWaitGL"></a><div class="titlepage"></div><div class="refnamediv"><h2>Name</h2><p>glXWaitGL — complete GL execution prior to subsequent X calls</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><h2>C Specification</h2><div class="funcsynopsis"><p><code class="funcdef">void <b class="fsfunc">glXWaitGL</b>(</code><var class="pdparam">void</var><code>)</code>;</p></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id432789"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            GL rendering calls made prior to <code class="function">glXWaitGL</code> are guaranteed to be
            executed before X rendering calls made after <code class="function">glXWaitGL</code>.
            Although this same result can be achieved using <a href="glFinish.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glFinish</span></span></a>,
            <code class="function">glXWaitGL</code> does not require a round trip to the server,
            and it is therefore more efficient in cases where client and server
            are on separate machines.
        </p><p>
            <code class="function">glXWaitGL</code> is ignored if there is no current GLX context.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id432839"></a><h2>Notes</h2><p>
            <code class="function">glXWaitGL</code> may or may not flush the X stream.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id432853"></a><h2>Errors</h2><p>
            <code class="constant">GLXBadCurrentWindow</code> is generated if the drawable associated
            with the current context of the calling thread is a window, and that
            window is no longer valid.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id419213"></a><h2>See Also</h2><p>
            <a href="glFinish.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glFinish</span></span></a>,
            <a href="glFlush.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glFlush</span></span></a>,
            <a href="glXWaitX.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXWaitX</span></span></a>,
            <code class="function">XSync</code>
